      • submit

        public PreparedBatch submit()
        Submit this statement to the batch, yielding the batch. The statement is already, actually part of the batch before it is submitted. This method is really just a convenient way to get the prepared batch back.
        Returns:
        the PreparedBatch which this is a part of
